description:
With all of us staying home during the pandemic, this can lead to increased problems with mental health and addiction. Including pornography. More and more studies are coming out about the dangers of pornography and its impact on relationships and mental health. This week on ANN In-Depth we look into what these dangers are and how we can help someone that's struggling. 

This week, we are joined by Pastor Bernie Anderson. For years, Pastor Anderson battled behind closed doors with pornography and sexual addiction. Exposed to pornography early in life, he was held captive by the addiction until he allowed God to transform his life.
